These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different pets are kept: snake, cat, frog, chinchilla
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, australian, mexican, russian
City: berlin, rome, marseilles, edinburgh
1. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the australian and the owner of the snake##2
3. the person traveling to rome is on the far left##1
4. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
5. the argentine is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
6. the mexican is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left or right of the owner of the cat##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet   | snake    | frog      | cat      | chinchilla    |
| Nationality   | russian | argentine | australian | mexican |
| City     | rome    | edinburgh       | marseilles     | berlin     |

