.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-2::.
There 4 different types of food: avocado, corn, cucumber, peach
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, r&b, country, indie
City: colone, hamburg, paris, liverpool
1. the fan of r&b is on the far left##1
2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating peach##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person eating corn##1
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
6. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |      4      |
| Food          | avocado     | peach     | corn       | cucumber    |
| Music-Genre         | r&b | country   | ambient | indie |
| City   | liverpool    | paris | hamburg    | colone        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, sudoku, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: fish, ferret, goldfish, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, climbing, cycling, sailing
1. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
3. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the owner of the fish##3
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby      | baking | collecting  | sudoku    | woodworking |
| Pet   | goldfish   | bird  | fish  | ferret    |
| Sport         | climbing    | sailing | baseball | cycling  |

