.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-4::.
City: venice, hamburg, paris, boston
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, family, time-travel
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, scooter, snowmobile, tram
1. the person driving the scooter is between the person watching drama movies and the person traveling to venice##2
2. the person watching action movies is on the left or right of the person watching drama movies##3
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person traveling to paris is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the van is the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
8. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |    3     |     4     |
| City          | paris   | venice     | hamburg | boston |
| Movie-Genre   | family | time-travel | action   | drama     |
| Transport           | tram | snowmobile      | scooter     | van       |

