.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, kiwi, mango, raspberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, board-games, woodworking, video-games
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, bird, lizard
1. the person eating eggplant is on the far right##1
2. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the owner of the horse##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person eating mango and the person eating kiwi##2
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
7. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
8. the person eating mango is the owner of the bird##1
9. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Food          | mango      | raspberry | kiwi      | eggplant |
| Hobby           | board-games | drawing | video-games | woodworking   |
| Pet   | bird    | lizard   | guinea-pig     | horse   |

