.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, entrepreneur, videographer
4 different games are played: domino, backgammon, go, bridge
There 4 different types of food: radish, lettuce, cherry, grapes
1. the person eating lettuce is the coach##1
2. the person eating cherry is the person playing bridge##1
3. the coach is on the left of the person eating radish##1
4. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person eating cherry##3
5. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person eating lettuce##3
6. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
7. the doctor is on the right of the person playing domino##1
8. the doctor is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3       |      4       |
| Job           | coach    | doctor   | entrepreneur | videographer |
| Game   | domino     | go   | bridge         | backgammon        |
| Food         | lettuce | radish | cherry         | grapes       |

