.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, soul, hip-hop, gospel
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, fanta, cola, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, japanese, mexican
 1. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3
 2. the japanese is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
 3. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
 4. the person drinking cola is on the right of the japanese##1
 5. the japanese is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 6. the fan of hip-hop is the fan of hip-hop##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
 8. the japanese is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 9. the american is on the right of the fan of soul##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
11. the person drinking fanta is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop    | r&b  | soul | gospel   |
| Beverage           | hot-chocolate | fanta   | cola    | milk |
| Nationality   | mexican      | japanese | brazilian | american  |

