.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-8::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, trike, snowmobile
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, hiking, magic-tricks
City: berlin, miami, boston, nizza
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
2. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
6. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |      4      |
| Transport          | trike | helicopter    | snowmobile | bus    |
| Hobby         | hiking     | magic-tricks | dancing  | board-games |
| City   | miami    | nizza      | berlin   | boston         |

