.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, sprite, tea, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, van, quad-bike, ship
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: indie, jazz, r&b, disco
1. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking water##1
7. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
8. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2        |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | sprite    | tea            | water     | fanta      |
| Transport           | trike    | ship | quad-bike     | van |
| Music-Genre   | indie | r&b    | jazz | disco    |

