.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, ebony, white, purple
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, horror, thriller
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, trike, boat, jet-ski
1. the person watching horror movies is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who likes white##1
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
4. the person who likes purple is on the far right##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is the person who likes purple##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
8. the person who likes ebony is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color          | ebony   | white | turquise | purple |
| Movie-Genre   | horror   | crime     | action      | thriller  |
| Transport   | subway | trike   | boat    | jet-ski   |

