.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-11::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, old-henry, oliveros
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, comedy, drama, scientific
There 4 different types of food: lemon, grapes, plum, papaya
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1
2. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
3. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
6. the person watching animation movies is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
7. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
8. the person eating lemon is the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2       |     3      |   4    |
| Cigar           | oliveros | pall-mall        | bluemaster   | old-henry  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy             | animation     | scientific | drama  |
| Food         | grapes           | papaya | lemon   | plum |

