.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, soy-milk, sprite
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, mauve, emerald, apricot
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, apple, blueberry, papaya
1. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
2. the person eating apple is on the far left##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who likes emerald##3
6. the person eating papaya is between the person eating apple and the person drinking mirinda##2
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who likes mauve##1
8. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |        1        |     2      |     3      |   4    |
| Beverage    | hot-chocolate   | soy-milk   | mirinda    | sprite |
| Color         | mauve | emerald    | blood-red      | apricot |
| Food   | apple      | papaya | blueberry | asparagus   |

