The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, reggae, dubstep, country
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, snowmobile, train
1. the person watching epic movies is the person driving the car##1
2. the fan of gospel is between the person watching comedy movies and the fan of country##2
3. the fan of reggae is the person driving the train##1
4. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
5. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is the fan of dubstep##1
7. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
8. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre    | comedy      | epic | zombie       | satire  |
| Music-Genre       | dubstep | gospel | country    | reggae |
| Transport   | scooter     | car         | snowmobile | train     |

