4. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the ferret and the owner of the hedgehog##2
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left or far right##3
6. the gothic-revival house is on the far left##1
7. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
8. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4      |
| Beverage    | juice   | lemonade    | coffee      | almond-milk |
| House       | gothic-revival  | farmhouse | art-deco | cottage     |
