.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, disco, house, soul
4 different games are played: bridge, whist, billiard, mah-jongg
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, golf, skateboarding, surfing
1. the fan of soul is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the fan of soul##1
4. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of disco##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the fan of punk and the fan of house##2
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
7. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
8. the fan of house is on the left or right of the person playing billiard##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |    3     |       4        |
| Music-Genre    | house | disco  | punk  | soul           |
| Game     | bridge | billiard | whist   | mah-jongg |
| Sport   | surfing   | golf       | biathlon | skateboarding  |

 